fit in this bag.03 \- Also, Amazon sells these cool \"PowerPax Storacell Slim Line\" AA battery caddies \& they work great.  Their orange color will make a nice contrast and they have many other colors available\?04 \- Another nice thing about this camera is that the insides, actually have markings for the proper way to face your memory card \& batteries. My SX260 doesn\'t, so if I haven\'t used it for awhile \(markings would be helpful\?\). The A1400 can also use the higher capacity SDXC, eXtra capacity memory card. For me, this newer SDXC card is great, 64 or 128GB, you can movie forever. Yet, my old VISTA system isn\'t fond of it, I have to use one of those USB computer cords to download \(AMAZON, sells an A1400 cord for around \$6.00\). It immediately loads the \(JPEC \& MOV\), no problem. Then, I\'ll double\-click the \"MOV\" and Apples Quicktime will convert, I\'ll login to Utube where the movie file is converted to an \"MP4\" format, so easier to manage\!05 \- Lastly, sometimes you might be taking pics around water \(a boat ride under the Golden Gate or the surf around some rocky beach \- lots of spray\), nevermind it might be one of those drizzle days\? If your just taking tourist or web shots, why risk getting moisture on the lens or in\-between the zoom mechanism of your best camera, use the A1400 \(16.1 megapixels\) ain\'t bad and I\'m thinking of buying another \(just for this reason alone\?\).\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-SX280\:1080p\/60p Full HD videoWith the camera\'s advanced DIGIC 6 Image Processor enabling \"MP4\" format recording, the PowerShot SX280 HS lets you shoot video at a selectable frame rate of 60 fps or 30 fps. 1080p\/60p Full HD video is extraordinarily smooth and rich in playback, ensuring that your important memories and creative film clips look their absolute best. Video recorded at 30 fps has also been improved through the combination of the DIGIC 6 Image Processor and Fine Movie Detail Processing, with reduced noise and high resolution.\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-\-", positive
